{
    "Abs":
    {
        "Introductions":
        [
            "============================================================================",
            "DESCRIPTION: Replace Abs with Max and Mul operations",
            "============================================================================",
            "This transformation pattern replaces an Abs operation with an equivalent",
            "computation using two basic operations: Mul and Max.",

            "MATHEMATICAL EQUIVALENCE:",
            "Abs(x) = Max(x, -x)",

            "TRANSFORMATION STEPS:",
            "1. Create a negation of the original input using Mul with -1",
            "2. Compare the original input and the negated input using Max",
            "3. Remove the original Abs node",

            "BENEFITS:",
            "- Enables backends that may not support Abs to use basic arithmetic operations",
            "- Supports decomposition for hardware with limited Abs support",
            "- Preserves semantic equivalence of the original Abs operation",

            "PRECONDITIONS:",
            "- Input tensor must be compatible with elementwise Mul and Max",

            "EXAMPLE:",
            "Input: x = [1.0, -2.0, 0.5]",
            "Original Abs computation:",
            "  Abs(x) = [1.0, 2.0, 0.5]",
            "Decomposed computation:",
            "  Mul:        neg_x = x * -1 = [-1.0, 2.0, -0.5]",
            "  Max:        output = Max(x, neg_x) = [1.0, 2.0, 0.5]",
            "Result: Equivalent output preserved by Mul and Max operations",

            "RESULT: Equivalent computation using atomic operations instead of Abs",
            "============================================================================"
        ],
        "SearchBy":
        {
            "nodes": [
                {
                    "op_type": "Abs"
                }
            ]
        },
        "ReplaceBy":
        {
            "graph": {
                "initializers": [
                    {
                        "name": "mul_initializer",
                        "shape": [1],
                        "data": [-1],
                        "data_type": "GetDataType({node.input[0]})"
                    }
                ],
                "nodes": [
                    {
                        "name": "{node.name}",
                        "Action": "Remove"
                    },
                    {
                        "name": "Mul_replace_for_{node.name}_{node.index}",
                        "op_type": "Mul",
                        "inputs": [
                            "{node.input[0]}",
                            "mul_initializer"
                        ],
                        "outputs": [
                            "Mul_replace_for_{node.name}_{node.index}_output"
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "name": "Max_replace_for_{node.name}_{node.index}",
                        "op_type": "Max",
                        "inputs": [
                            "{node.input[0]}",
                            "Mul_replace_for_{node.name}_{node.index}_output"
                        ],
                        "outputs": [
                            "{node.output[0]}"
                        ]
                    }
                ]
            }
        }
    }
}